eligibility_key2: Election ke samay par jin students ko NavGurukul me **2 month ya usse jyada** samay ho chuka hai, wo **council** election me contest kar sakte hain. Ye niyam laagu nahi hoga agar kisi pro`file` ke liye 3 se kam candidates contest karte hain.
eligibility_key3: Election ke samay jis student ko NavGurukul me **6 months ya usse jyada** ho chuka hai aur jo ek baar (current ya past me) council member reh chuka hai, wo **GenSec** ki pro`file` ke liye contest kar sakta hai.
eligibility_key4: Aise case me, agar humaare paas kisi pro`file` ke liye 3 candidates nahi hote hain to election me contest karne ke eligibility criteria ko 1 month kam kar diya jayega.
